<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">Current time in a more human-readable format is very helpful sometimes. Also, the exit status of the previous command, if nonzero, is also very helpful when anything fails.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44369984&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44364874%2344369984" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
