<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">You could probably (I haven’t tested it) append the run time as a comment to the history using something like PROMPT_COMMAND and `history -r &lt;(…)`, instead of cluttering the prompt with it. And the start time is already in the history, using HISTTIMEFORMAT.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44369209&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44364874%2344369209" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
