<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">As an alternative, perennial HN recommendation atuin (<a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;atuin.sh" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;atuin.sh</a>) logs time, duration and exit code (among other data) for every command.<p>That way you only have to look at it when you need it, and you can also figure out what you were doing last week&#x2F;month&#x2F;year if necessary.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44367249&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44364874%2344367249" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
