<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">That&#x27;s a good reason to have timestamps in the history, which you should.<p>Something like<p><pre><code>  export HISTFILESIZE=
  export HISTSIZE=
  export HISTTIMEFORMAT=&quot;[%F %T] &quot;
  shopt -s histappend
</code></pre>
really ought to be default in bash.<p>It&#x27;s not as clear why you need it in the interactive prompt.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44368978&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44364874%2344368978" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
