<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">I&#x27;m senior, been working in the industry for closing on 25 years now.  I usually avoid anything &quot;ohh shiny&quot;.<p>For most of my career I used a very simple PS1:<p><pre><code>    export PS1=&quot;\[\033[1;32m\][\t \u@\h \w]\\$\[\033[0m\] &quot;
